{"tid":1232210,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"梁凌杰先生，多謝您用自己生命燃亮香港。","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:33:51.000Z","uid":193485,"like":207,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdb8c9caef76eb6c22e19b5e7fc2eaeed1adcc0","tid":1232210,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"見到今日遊行，香港真的好美。<br />\n<br />\n多謝您對香港既愛、以死明志既勇氣、舍生取義既意志，犧牲自己既生命去燃亮香港。<br />\n<br />\n歷史會記住您對香港既付出，願您一路好走，可以係一個擁有真正民主自由既理想國度生活。<br />\n願永垂不朽。<br />\n<br />\n最後借分享一位連登巴打整既兩張圖，真係整得好靚，一睇到，眼淚就莫名其妙的流落嚟....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVVMEDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVVMEDz.png&h=fdb42846&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAgghqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAgghqf.png&h=6629a124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a31b95aebaa31eaeee3a702205c9f38132b37be9","tid":1232210,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"搵唔返嗰位巴打既post, 有冇人可以貼出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd40a16b376fb0b8e2f13cc2f8b1fec95086c77e","tid":1232210,"uid":186152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"Respect, rip"},{"pid":"14c83eca66b69d22e5f26d0b3765f36a8d1b9c87","tid":1232210,"uid":235418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"06267dadaa96c0e5772b576f389080cd0943d803","tid":1232210,"uid":111354,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"[梁凌杰千古] 梁山好漢嚎滿城 凌雲壯志喚我民 杰為卓犖召眾魂 千秋萬世為人記 古調獨彈永不再<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1232045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1232045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f749da5dd5853d0b33a11cc236db3056b260346","tid":1232210,"uid":193485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06267dadaa96c0e5772b576f389080cd0943